And they want to know what various churches teach.

00:01:17.230 --> 00:01:21.230
And as she was investigating the teaching of various religions,

00:01:21.230 --> 00:01:23.230
she noticed that there were a lot of negative comments

00:01:23.230 --> 00:01:26.230
about Jehovah's Witnesses.

00:01:26.230 --> 00:01:31.230
Did that stop her? No, because she was a fair-minded person.

00:01:31.230 --> 00:01:35.230
So she went online and found our website.

00:01:35.230 --> 00:01:41.230
And she found the frequently asked questions section of the website.

00:01:41.230 --> 00:01:43.230
And she loved it.

00:01:43.230 --> 00:01:47.230
Every question was answered with the Bible.

00:01:47.230 --> 00:01:50.230
And that's what she wanted in a religion.

00:01:50.230 --> 00:01:53.230
Well, she noticed on our website that there was an invitation

00:01:53.230 --> 00:01:55.230
to attend our meetings.

00:01:55.230 --> 00:01:58.230
And so she talked to schoolmate into going with her to the Kingdom Hall.

00:01:58.230 --> 00:02:00.230
She was a schoolgirl.

00:02:00.230 --> 00:02:04.230
Now, she loved what she heard at the Kingdom Hall,

00:02:04.230 --> 00:02:07.230
and she was so warmly welcomed.

00:02:07.230 --> 00:02:12.229
But wouldn't you know it? Her parents were opposed.

00:02:12.229 --> 00:02:16.229
And soon after she made that one foray to the Kingdom Hall,

00:02:16.229 --> 00:02:19.229
they moved to an isolated area where there were none

00:02:19.229 --> 00:02:22.229
of Jehovah's Witnesses.

00:02:22.229 --> 00:02:29.229
And Kaja was caught off from any association with the Witnesses for one year.

00:02:29.229 --> 00:02:33.229
But not to be deterred.

00:02:33.229 --> 00:02:38.229
She studied all of our publications on the website.

00:02:38.229 --> 00:02:41.229
And she kept up to date with the truth.

00:02:41.229 --> 00:02:47.229
In September of 2014, she was again able to make contact with the Witnesses

00:02:47.229 --> 00:02:49.229
and she accepted a Bible study.

00:02:49.229 --> 00:02:54.229
And in July 2015, she was baptized.

00:02:54.229 --> 00:02:55.229
So she got the truth.

00:02:55.229 --> 00:03:01.229
Her initial contact with the truth was on at www.org.

00:03:01.229 --> 00:03:04.229
Now, speaking of being cut off from the Witnesses,

00:03:04.229 --> 00:03:06.229
that's Kenji's problem.

00:03:06.229 --> 00:03:08.229
He's a 15-year-old boy in Japan.

00:03:08.229 --> 00:03:12.229
He would love to attend meetings at the Kingdom Hall.

00:03:12.229 --> 00:03:15.229
