Another negative comment about Jehovah's Witnesses.

00:04:38.610 --> 00:04:39.610
What did she do?

00:04:39.610 --> 00:04:42.610
She went home and she went online.

00:04:42.610 --> 00:04:45.610
And she found her website.

00:04:45.610 --> 00:04:52.610
For five months, she carefully studied all of the material on our website.

00:04:52.610 --> 00:04:55.610
