00:07:29.610 --> 00:07:32.610
So now there were a lot of challenges to overcome.

00:07:32.610 --> 00:07:35.610
It wasn't so easy, but he persevered.

00:07:35.610 --> 00:07:41.610
And in June of 2014, he left the church, he left the monastery,

00:07:41.610 --> 00:07:47.610
and then in the month of October of that same year, he was baptized as one of Jehovah's Witnesses,

00:07:47.610 --> 00:07:52.610
since he has served as an auxiliary pioneer.

